<p class="campus_location"><span class="label"><strong>Contact Information: </strong></span>
<br /><span class="campus_location">Campus Location: 1800 Student Services Building (SSB)
<br /><span class="phone">(312) 996-3126 Fax: (312) 996-3385</span>
